{@{
        ViewBag.Title = "The eConFix" ;
}
<h2>@ViewBag.Title</h2>
<h3>@ViewBag.Message</h3>

<!-- Styling for the About Us Page -->
<style>
    body {
       
        background-image: url('../../Images/Anotherblue.jpg');
        background-position: center;
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
        background-size: cover;
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        color: #fff;
    }

    h2, h3 {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 2.5em;
        margin-top: 30px;
        color: #fff;
    }

    h3 {
        font-size: 1.5em;
        margin-top: 10px;
        margin-bottom: 40px;
        color: #ddd;
    }

    .about-container {
        background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7); /* Semi-transparent dark background */
        padding: 40px;
        margin: 40px auto;
        border-radius: 12px;
        max-width: 900px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
    }

        .about-container p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            line-height: 1.8em;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: #f1f1f1;
        }

        .about-container ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding-left: 0;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            line-height: 1.8em;
            color: #ddd;
        }

        .about-container li {
            padding-left: 20px;
            position: relative;
        }

            .about-container li::before {
                content: '✔'; /* Using check mark bullet points */
                position: absolute;
                left: 0;
                top: 0;
                color: #00aaff;
                font-size: 1.4em;
            }

        .about-container h2 {
            font-size: 2.2em;
            margin-top: 40px;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .about-container ul li:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
</style>

<!-- About Us Content Section -->
<div class="about-container">
    <p>
        eConFix is an online platform that offers a wide range of construction and maintenance services.
        Through our website, users can easily book the required service and make secure payments online. Once the service is booked, our skilled team will visit the customer's site to deliver the services requested.
    </p>

    <ul>
        <li>Construction industry delivery capability for South Africa’s social and economic growth</li>
        <li>A proudly South African construction industry that delivers to globally competitive standards</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>As the cidb, we focus on:</h2>

    <ul>
        <li>Sustainable growth, capacity development, and empowerment</li>
        <li>Improved industry performance and best practices</li>
        <li>A transformed industry, underpinned by consistent and ethical procurement practices</li>
        <li>Enhanced value to clients and society</li>
    </ul>
</div>

